<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.7">
<l>kaṟantanaṟ pālun tayiruṅ kaṭaintuṟi mēlvaitta veṇṇey</l>
<l>piṟantatu vēmuta lākap peṟṟaṟi yēṉempi rāṉē</l>
<l>ciṟantanaṟ ṟāyalar tūṟṟu meṉpata ṉāṟpiṟar muṉṉē</l>
<l>maṟantu muraiyāṭa māṭṭēṉ mañcaṉa māṭanī vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My lord! Since the first [day of your] birth,</l>
<l>I do not know of churned butter placed in pots,</l>
<l>nor of curds nor milk freshly milked.</l>
<l>Even if I forget [myself] in front of others,</l>
<l rend="indent">because of their spreading gossip</l>
<l rend="indent">about [your] eminent birth mother,</l>
<l>I am not able to speak a word [of this].</l>
<l>Come take your ceremonial bath!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
